KAMAGUGU &#8211; A taxi overturned on the Kamagugu Road with school children inside it. According to department of Safety and Security spokesman Mr Joseph Mabuza, the accident occurred at around 14:00. This after the back tyre of the taxi came off and the driver lost control of the vehicle.Thirteen slightly injured learners from KaMagugu Inclusive School were transported to Rob Ferreira hospital.Read more here: Five-year-old and two adults die in head on collision on R532&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;